Learnt Group BY:
1. Count the number of patients by each service.
  Sol: use challenge;
SELECT Service,count(patient_id) as Numberofpatients from patients
group by service;



2. Calculate the average age of patients grouped by service.

  Sol: Use challenge;
SELECT Service, avg(age) as AVG_AGE from patients
group by service;
3. Find the total number of staff members per role.
use challenge;
SELECT Role,count(staff_id) as numbers from staff
group by role;

Challenge:
For each hospital service, calculate the total number of patients admitted, total patients refused, and the admission rate (percentage of requests that were admitted). Order by admission rate descending.
Sol:
Use challenge;
SELECT Service,sum(patients_admitted) AS Admitted,sum(patients_refused) as Refused,round((sum(patients_admitted)/sum(patients_request))*100,1) as Pctofrequestadmitted from services_weekly
group by service;
